  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 137.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第137课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "A Pleasant Dream.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "美好的梦。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "What would Julie like to do if she had the money?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "如果朱莉有了钱，她想做什么？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Are you doing the football pools, Brian?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "布赖恩，你在填足球赛博彩单吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "Yes, I've nearly finished, Julie.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "是的，我快填完了，朱莉。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "I'm sure we'll win something this week.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我相信我们这周会赢点什么。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "You always say that, but we never win anything.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你总是这么说，可我们从来什么也没赢过。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "What will you do if you win a lot of money?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "如果你赢了很多钱，你会做什么？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "If I win a lot of money, I'll buy you a mink coat.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "如果我赢了很多钱，我会给你买一件貂皮大衣。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "I don't want a mink coat.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我不想要貂皮大衣。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "I want to see the world.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我想环游世界。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "All right.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "好吧。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "If we win a lot of money, we'll travel around the world and we'll stay at the best hotels.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "如果我们赢了很多钱，我们就环游世界，住最好的酒店。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "Then we'll return home and buy a big house in the country.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "然后我们回国，在乡下买一栋大房子。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "We'll have a beautiful garden and… But if we spend all that money, we'll be poor again.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们会有一个漂亮的花园，而且……可是，如果我们把钱全花光，就又会变穷。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "What will we do then?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那时我们怎么办？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "If we spend all the money, we'll try and win the football pools again.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "如果把钱全花光了，我们就再去赢一次足球赛博彩。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "It's a pleasant dream, but everything depends on if.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这个梦很美好，但一切都取决于那个“如果”。"
      }
    }
  ],
